description: This file defines React components for a UI Card, including Card, CardHeader, and CardBody, used for rendering card-like UI elements with optional header and content sections.

methods.name: Card
methods.description: A simple card container component that wraps children content with optional additional className.

methods.name: CardHeader
methods.description: A component for rendering a header section of a card, including title, optional subtitle, and optional actions.

methods.name: CardBody
methods.description: A container component for the main content area of a card.
